<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>YEMS Tools</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --bg2: #1e293b;
      --card: #f8fafc;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --accent: #0ea5e9;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, var(--bg), var(--bg2));
      color: #fff;
    }
    .wrap { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    p { opacity: 0.85; }
    .grid {
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    }
    .card {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: var(--card);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      border: 1px solid #dbe3ee;
    }
    .card h2 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .card p { margin: 0; color: #334155; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>YEMS Runtime Pages</h1>
    <p>Split by concern. Public status is separate from authenticated technician tools.</p>

    <section class="grid">
      <a class="card" href="/status">
        <h2>Public Status</h2>
        <p>Read-only latency overview (p95, p99, total requests).</p>
        <span class="badge">Public</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/auth">
        <h2>Auth Test</h2>
        <p>Login and basic authenticated route checks.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/technician">
        <h2>Technician Tools</h2>
        <p>Deep logs and RBAC policy inspection (token required).</p>
        <span class="badge">Technician / Platform Admin</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/test">
        <h2>Test Section</h2>
        <p>Seeded RBAC accounts + embedded Grafana dashboard.</p>
        <span class="badge">QA / Demo</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
